                        <interp inst="t18380226-name-1092" type="surname" value="KING"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380226-name-1092" type="given" value="THOMAS HOBBS"></interp>THOMAS HOBBS KING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I received charge of the prisoner, and took the property.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced, and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was walking along the square, and saw these things—I did not know who they belonged to—I took them up, and some<lb></lb>body cried "Stop thief."</p>
               <p>
